          <p class="mt-3 leading-relaxed text-bark-muted">Chengxian founded SmartPetGuide in 2026 after realizing most pet product reviews either lacked real data or pushed affiliate links without transparency. He leads all research and content at SmartPetGuide — analyzing thousands of verified Amazon reviews, cross-referencing owner experiences from Reddit and forums, and comparing product specs to produce honest, evidence-based recommendations. His work has been cited in Wikidata and syndicated across Medium and Pinterest.</p>
          <p class="mt-2 leading-relaxed text-bark-muted">Every review, comparison, and guide on SmartPetGuide is researched and written directly by Chengxian, following a structured methodology of verified review aggregation, owner experience synthesis, and cost-of-ownership analysis. No AI-generated fluff, no outsourced content, no paid rankings.</p>
